China Plans Center for Climate Change Study, 21st Herald Says

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-09-05T23:45:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-05/china-plans-center-for-climate-change-study-21st-herald-says.html
China’s National Development and
Reform Commission plans to set up a center for the strategic
study of and international cooperation on climate change, the
21st Century Business Herald reported, citing an unidentified
person at the nation’s top economic planning agency.  The establishment of the center has been approved and it
may open by the end of this year, the newspaper reported today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bloomberg News at 
 jliu42@bloomberg.net  